**Setting up the environment:**

[Download Oracle Java 17 LTS](https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/#java17)

Place in "Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/"

Install JAVA_HOME in the terminal: `export JAVA_HOME=/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk-17.0.4.1.jdk/Contents/Home`

Install HomeBrew with the command in the terminal: `/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"`

Install Maven 3.8.6 with a command in the terminal: `brew install maven`
